Paul Préboist https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Pr%C3%A9boist 0 Paul Préboist (21 February 1927 – 4 March 1997) was a French actor. He made his film debut in Cresus (1960). Appeared in more than hundred films, mostly in supporting roles, and is best known as a comic actor. Paul_Préboist ( 21 February_1927 – 4_March_1997 ) was a_French_actor .
